        rdfs:comment      "Automated change 2024-03-14: GO:0099061 replaced by GO:0098839" , "Rationale: Fig. 5: \"Electron micrographs showing immunogold staining for GluR4 in the reticular nucleus\"\n- \"Gold particles coding for GluR2/3 and GluR4 exhibited similar overall distributions .... Labeling was concentrated over the postsynaptic density, postsynaptic membranes, and synaptic cleft of a large fraction of asymmetric synapses\"\n\n- Based on the known transmembrane topology of the protein, the \"integral component of ... membrane\" term was chosen.. Experimental description: \"Male Sprague-Dawley rats (200-350 g), deeply anesthetized with Nembutal (sodium pentibarbitone 60 mg/kg, i.p.),...\"" ;
